summary: This mod adds new fences to different locations throughout Skyrim. Most of them are residing in caves or hidden passages within some towns.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds new fences to different locations throughout Skyrim. Most of them are residing in caves or hidden passages within some towns. 

This mod adds several different fences and you MUST be in the Thieves guild to be able to use. 

The fences are in: 
Whiterun 
Windhelm 
Winterhold 
Solitude 
Dawnstar 

Hope you enjoy and endorse if you like!
author: guitarman007
